- Syntax of this file is:
- One char command, whitespace, command parameters
- Lines starts with '-', ' ', '#', '/' are treated as comments
- D Directory to create
- F File to copy
- S Script file (exec after install, then remove it)
- A Archive file (auto gz when pack, auto ungz when unpack)
- E Execute file (F + 'chmod +x')
- Q Sql script (exec SQL text after install, then remove it)
- X E + A
- I Information line, installer after unpack path
- M Md5 hash of all files (auto done when pack)
- Other chars at line start treated as illegal line
